      <title>高盛前合伙人筹集 16 亿美元用于直接贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/ex-goldman-partners-amass-1-6-billion-for-direct-lending-effort</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私人信贷公司 5C Investment Partners 由两位前高盛集团合伙人共同创立，将在为高级直接贷款交易筹集 16 亿美元后开始投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/ex-goldman-partners-amass-1-6-billion-for-direct-lending-effort</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司启动 190 亿美元股票出售计划，以阻止降级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/boeing-launches-19-billion-share-sale-to-boost-liquidity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司启动了一项近 190 亿美元的股票出售计划，这是上市公司历史上规模最大的股票出售计划之一，旨在解决这家陷入困境的飞机制造商的流动性需求，并避免其信用评级可能被下调至垃圾级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/boeing-launches-19-billion-share-sale-to-boost-liquidity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 10:54:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列避开伊朗袭击能源目标，欧洲天然气供应下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/europe-gas-slips-as-israel-avoids-energy-targets-in-iran-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列对伊朗目标的袭击避开了石油、核能和民用基础设施，导致欧洲天然气价格下跌，表明与中东冲突相关的供应风险目前仍在控制之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/europe-gas-slips-as-israel-avoids-energy-targets-in-iran-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 07:31:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国财报最繁忙的一周伊始，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在企业财报发布最为繁忙的一周中，股市开始上涨，交易员们也为三份备受瞩目的经济报告做准备，这些报告将为美联储的下一次决策奠定基础。油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 22:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本周全球大宗商品值得关注的五大关键图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财报季即将到来，英国石油公司将于周二公布石油巨头第三季度的财报。与此同时，黄金生产商的财报也纷至沓来。在农业方面，全球使用最广泛的植物油价格飙升，再次引发人们对食品通胀的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
